Blog.post:
    
       
      Today me and Badri came up with this universal ABBA code, which can remove the Blogger Banner completely from any template !!! All u need to do is, just put following peice of code in your template right after the
 
   <style type="text/css">
 
line.

 
 

 
 
/* 
 *  by : Parikshit & Badri
 *  to : Add Block to Block Ad in Blogger.com !!! 
*/

div {display:none}
#wrapper {display:block}
#wrapper div {display:block}

/*Following lines fix the IE margin bug */
#wrapper div#sidebar-wrapper {display: inline}
#wrapper div#main-content {display: inline}
